modName: Slim to Busty - CBBE preset for Bodyslide
descriptionHtml:
The title explains itself. This preset for Bodyslide ranges to slim (Weight 0) to busty (Weight 100).
 
There is 2 files : the first, "Slim and Busty" is for nude bodies and some clothes ; the second one, "Slim and Busty bis" is for the most of the armors (the "push-up" effect). Of course you're free, for instance, to use the first file for all armors. It's up to you ! ;)
